  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    A guide for authorised persons
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    This document provides authorised persons with advice on their role at marriage ceremonies and how to keep accurate records.
  </p>

